Orientation Session for Analytics and Finance Clubs

Body:
Greetings from the Career Development Team, I&AR!


Do terms like investment banking, stocks, big data and machine learning
excite you? In today's competitive world, it is essential that we have an
edge over others. Realizing which, we kick off the activities of the
Finance and Analytics Clubs for this year.


The clubs have planned a lot of new initiatives and programs to bring out
the best in you and provide exposure to the industry. Look out for
interactive case studies, discussions, projects and networking with experts
from these fields.


To know more about the activities of the clubs and to be a part of either
club, join us for the orientation session this Monday.


Date: 22nd August, 2016
Time: 6 pm



The orientation session will be followed by the introductory lecture of
the Analytics Club  'Big Data: Applications in Industry' byMr. Kapi
l
Kumar, a Big Data Engineer from American Express. If you want to get a
better picture about what goes an in an Analytics firm, do attend.


Details regarding venue will be intimated soon through mail.



